---
title: Soy-Glazed Steak with Asparagus Stir-Fry plus Jasmine Rice & Scallion-Ginger Oil
description: This stir-fry is a flavor supernova! The star? Steak that you’ll sear, slice, and drizzle with a glossy soy glaze amped up with sweet chili sauce and nutty sesame dressing. Sprinkle that steak with crackly sesame seeds and serve it alongside a stir-fry of asparagus, scallion, and onion. Fluffy jasmine rice elevated with aromatic scallion-ginger oil rounds out this explosion of deliciousness.
